<title>UK: BZW sets warrants on French midcap growth basket.</title>
<headline>BZW sets warrants on French midcap growth basket.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-02-07</dateline>
<text>
<p>BZW Warrants Ltd has issued 500,000 American-style call warrants, on a French midcap growth basket comprising BIC, Rexel, SEB, Castorama, Primagaz, Guilbert, Zodiac L and Clarins, lead manager BZW Securities Ltd said.</p>
<p>10 warrants control one basket.</p>
<p> STRIKE PRICE    15,000.00 FRF	   ISSUE PRICE  147.00 FRF</p>
<p> MATURITY DATE   30.JAN.99		 PAYDATE	27.FEB.97</p>
<p> LISTING	   PARIS		     MIN EXER LOT 200</p>
<p> SPOT REFERENCE  14,738.00 FRF</p>
<p>--Reuter London Newsroom +44 171 542 7658</p>
